  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN198.2-kilavi">iravukkuṟi (C2: /) puṇarntu nīṅkiya talaimakaḷatu pōkku nōkkiyatalaimakaṉ taṉṉeñciṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What HE said to his heart when looking at HER going [away] who was leaving after the union in a night tryst.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN198.2">
        <l>kūṟuvaṅ kollō kūṟalaṅ kolleṉak</l>
        <l>karanta kāmaṅ kainniṟuk kalātu</l>
        <l>nayantunām viṭṭa naṉmoḻi nampi</l>
        <l>yaraināḷ yāmattu viḻu<supplied>ma</supplied>ḻai karantu</l>
        <l>kārmalar kamaḻuṅ kūntaṟ ṟūviṉai</l>
        <l>nuṇṇū lākam poruntiṉaḷ veṟpi</l>
        <l>ṉiḷamaḻai cūḻnta maṭamayil pōla</l>
        <l>vaṇṭuvaḻip paṭara taṇmalar vēyntu</l>
        <l>vilvakup puṟṟa nalvāṅku kuṭaccū</l>
        <l>lañcilam poṭukki yañci<supplied>ṉa</supplied>ḷ vantu</l>
        <l>tuñcā yāmattu muyaṅkiṉaḷ peyarvō</l>
        <l>ḷāṉṟa kaṟpiṟ cāṉṟa pēriya</l>
        <l>lammā varivaiyō valla ṭeṉāa</l>
        <l>tāay naṉṉā ṭaṇaṅkuṭaic cilampiṟ</l>
        <l>kavuriyam pēriya vurukeḻu <supplied>ka</supplied>vāa</l>
        <l>ṉērmalar niṟaiccuṉai yuṟaiyuñ</l>
        <l>cūrmakaṇ mātō veṉṉumeṉ ṉeñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Besides weighing in hand the hidden passion: (2)</l>
        <l>“shall we talk? Shall we not talk?”, (1)</l>
        <l>longingly trusting in the good word uttered by us, (3)</l>
        <l>hiding in the excellent rains of deep midnight, (4)</l>
        <l>she with a bosom suited [to wearing] fine threads (6a-c)</l>
        <l>of pure workmanship, tresses fragrant with the blossoms of the rainy season, (5)</l>
        <l>covered with cool flowers, so that bees make [their] way [to them], (8)</l>
        <l>like a youthful peacock surrounded by young clouds on the mountain, (6df.)</l>
        <l>she who out of fear had muffled [the sound of her] pretty anklets (10a-c)</l>
        <l>of the well-curved Kuṭaccūl type that has bow[like-] divisions, (9)</l>
        <l>came [and] embraced [me] at sleepless midnight [and then] went back. (10df.)</l>
        <l>“She is, is she not, that dark woman (13a-c)</l>
        <l>of great nature abounding in noble fidelity? (12)</l>
        <l>Or is she a woman sprite (17ab)</l>
        <l>who dwells in a pool full of beautiful blossoms (16)</l>
        <l>on the fearful slope named Kavuriyam (15)</l>
        <l>of the haunted mountain side in the good land of Āay in the South?” (13df.)</l>
        <l rend="indent8">says my heart. (17cd)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
